value:
Multiplex network consisting of 5 edge types corresponding to online and offline relationships (Facebook, leisure, work, co-authorship, lunch) between employees of the Computer Science department at Aarhus.  Data hosted by Manlio De Domenico.[^icon]
[^icon]: Description obtained from the [ICON](https://icon.colorado.edu) project.
['Matteo Magnani, Barbora Micenkova, and Luca Ross, \Combinatorial Analysis of Multiple Networks.\" arXiv:1303.4986 (2013)
